OL,3,CUnion warns urgent action is needed to
OL,4,Crecruit more consultants
OL,6,FWords by Representing Border's Gregory
OL,7,FHoare.
OL,9,FThe union representing doctors in
OL,10,FScotland has warned that urgent action
OL,11,Fis needed to recruit more consultants
OL,12,Fin Dumfries and Galloway and the
OL,13,FScottish Borders.
OL,15,FFreedom of Information requests by ITV
OL,16,FBorder show that around seven per cent
OL,17,Fof the total number of consultant
OL,18,Fposts in NHS Borders are vacant.
OL,20,FMost of those - five per cent - have
OL,21,Fbeen empty for over a year.
