OL,3,CUnion warns urgent action is needed to
OL,4,Crecruit more consultants
OL,6,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway referred us
OL,7,Fto workforce data from September 2024,
OL,8,Fwhen around 10 per cent of posts for
OL,9,Fsenior doctors were vacant.
OL,11,FOnce again, the statistics suggest
OL,12,Fthis was not a short-term issue, as
OL,13,F7.6% of roles had been unfilled for at
OL,14,Fleast six months.
OL,16,FAcross Scotland, around six percent of
OL,17,Fconsultant posts were vacant in
OL,18,FSeptember 2024, demonstrating that the
OL,19,Fissue is worse in the south of
OL,20,FScotland.
