OL,3,CUnion warns urgent action is needed to
OL,4,Crecruit more consultants
OL,6,FDoctor Joanna Bredski, Deputy Chair of
OL,7,Fthe British Medical Association's
OL,8,FScottish Consultants Committee, says
OL,9,Fthe vacancies are a "major problem",
OL,10,Fwhich lead to longer waiting times for
OL,11,Fpatients, and added pressure on staff.
OL,13,FRecruitment issues can also carry a
OL,14,Ffinancial burden for health boards.
OL,16,FFreedom of Information requests by
OL,17,FScottish Labour show that between 2019
OL,18,Fand 2024, NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,19,Fspent more than #60m on temporary
OL,20,Fconsultants, referred to as locums.
