OL,3,CUnion warns urgent action is needed to
OL,4,Crecruit more consultants
OL,6,FOver the same period, NHS Borders
OL,7,Fspent around #9m.
OL,9,FDoctor Bredski, who works as a
OL,10,Fconsultant psychiatrist in the
OL,11,FScottish Borders, says locums are
OL,12,Fnecessary when there are "unexpected
OL,13,Fshort-term gaps", but are an
OL,14,F"expensive sticking plaster that don't
OL,15,Ffix longer term issues."
OL,17,FIn a statement, NHS Dumfries and
OL,18,FGalloway said spending on locums was
OL,19,Fnecessary due to "ongoing challenges
OL,20,Fin recruiting to permanent posts".
