OL,3,CUnion warns urgent action is needed to
OL,4,Crecruit more consultants
OL,6,FThe health board said recruitment was
OL,7,Fone of its top priorities and that "a
OL,8,Fnumber of notable consultant posts"
OL,9,Fhave been filled in recent weeks.
OL,11,FThe Chief Executive of NHS Borders
OL,12,Fsaid recruitment challenges are "a
OL,13,Fconstraint" which has an impact on
OL,14,Fwaiting times.
OL,16,FPeter Moore said the Scottish Borders
OL,17,Fis a "beautiful place to work", and
OL,18,Fthat the health board is working hard
OL,19,Fto attract doctors to the area.
